00:53:32,751 --> 00:53:38,548
I felt a substantial amount of pain
that made me forget my sorrows.

525
00:53:50,560 --> 00:53:54,147
Yoon Seong-kyu must've suffered
hundredfold or thousandfold.

526
00:53:54,231 --> 00:53:55,106
Yes.

527
00:53:56,942 --> 00:53:59,402
You deserve that for killing my son.

528
00:54:01,279 --> 00:54:03,323
That was what I thought.

529
00:54:07,035 --> 00:54:08,870
But as time passed,

530
00:54:10,580 --> 00:54:11,831
I became afraid.

531
00:54:25,804 --> 00:54:27,973
I was afraid...

532
00:54:30,225 --> 00:54:31,434
that when that time came,

533
00:54:32,811 --> 00:54:36,314
I'd search for someone
who'd deliver me as well.

534
00:54:53,290 --> 00:54:54,207
And is that…

535
00:54:57,585 --> 00:54:58,795
Cha Yo-han?

536
00:55:08,054 --> 00:55:09,889
It doesn't matter who it is.

537
00:55:13,476 --> 00:55:16,021
Because if that time comes,

538
00:55:17,314 --> 00:55:20,734
not only will my body die...

539
00:55:23,486 --> 00:55:25,989
but my soul will die as well.

540
00:55:38,710 --> 00:55:41,129
The number you called cannot be reached…

541
00:55:49,679 --> 00:55:51,431
I've never seen this occur here.

542
00:55:51,514 --> 00:55:52,682
Me neither.

543
00:55:56,644 --> 00:55:59,439
They're currently conducting
the phlegm test.

544
00:56:00,523 --> 00:56:01,608
You got the results.

545
00:56:04,694 --> 00:56:06,196
His blood vessels are fine.

546
00:56:06,279 --> 00:56:08,448
Just like Dr. Cha said,
there is an abscess.

547
00:56:08,531 --> 00:56:10,992
We'll only know for sure once
the phlegm test result comes back.

548
00:56:11,076 --> 00:56:13,161
Judging by his symptoms
and the radiological findings,

549
00:56:13,244 --> 00:56:14,996
nocardiosis seems like our best bet.

550
00:56:15,080 --> 00:56:16,581
ACUTE OR CHRONIC INFECTION OF THE LUNGS

551
00:56:16,664 --> 00:56:19,793
The phlegm test result
won't come back anytime soon.

552
00:56:22,253 --> 00:56:23,588
Should we trust him and administer

553
00:56:23,671 --> 00:56:26,216
trimethoprim-sulfamethoxazole
and imipenem?

554
00:56:26,299 --> 00:56:28,176
A TYPE OF ANTIBIOTIC

555
00:56:30,345 --> 00:56:32,222
Let's do that.

556
00:56:32,305 --> 00:56:34,808
It's a tricky area, so we'll need
to discuss with Neurosurgery

557
00:56:34,891 --> 00:56:36,184
on the surgical removal.

558
00:56:36,267 --> 00:56:38,978
-Okay.
-Please tell Dr. Cha.

559
00:56:39,062 --> 00:56:40,397
Okay.

560
00:56:44,651 --> 00:56:46,319
Once Gi-seok recovers
due to this diagnosis,

561
00:56:46,403 --> 00:56:48,029
Dr. Cha's suspension will be lifted,
right?

562
00:56:48,905 --> 00:56:50,990
Isn't it ridiculous
to kick out someone so competent?

563
00:56:52,575 --> 00:56:53,535
You're right.

564
00:56:54,536 --> 00:56:55,912
-We should--
-I'll--

565
00:56:58,373 --> 00:57:00,208
I'll talk to Gi-seok's mother.

