for Dr. Cha.

585
00:59:33,570 --> 00:59:35,738
We've had problems
ever since he joined us.

586
00:59:35,822 --> 00:59:36,864
Let's deal with Dr. Cha.

587
00:59:36,948 --> 00:59:38,950
