590
00:59:42,954 --> 00:59:45,957
Isn't it strange?
They never recruit people like this.

591
00:59:46,040 --> 00:59:50,587
Something like the Cherubim video happens,
Death Talks could become a murder site.

592
00:59:57,176 --> 00:59:59,137
Don't you ever get sick.

